SUMMARY:Notice Of Public Meeting Tampa City Council Special Call Workshop
LOCATION:315 E. Kennedy Blvd. Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:NOTICE OF PUBLIC MEETING TAMPA CITY COUNCIL SPECIAL CALL WORKS
 HOP Date: Tuesday\, May 5\, 2026 Time: 5:00 PM Location: Old City Hall 315
  E. Kennedy Blvd. Tampa FL 33602 Agenda: https:tampa.govagendas (https:tam
 pa.govagendas) The public and citizens of the City of Tampa will be able t
 o watch\, listen or view this meeting on: Cable TV: Spectrum Channel 640 F
 rontier Channel 15 Internet: https:www.tampa.govlivestream (https:www.tamp
 a.govlivestream) The purpose of this Special Call Workshop is to discuss a
  Memorandum of Understanding regarding the Tampa Bay Rays. In-person publi
 c comment will be accepted at the end of the workshop\, three minutes per 
 speaker. In accordance with the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA) and 
 Section 286.26\, Florida Statutes\, persons with disabilities needing a re
 asonable accommodation to participate in this public hearing or meeting sh
 ould contact the City of Tampas ADA Coordinator at least 48 hours prior to
  the proceeding. The ADA Coordinator may be contacted via phone at 813-274
 -3964\, email at TampaADAtampagov.net\, or by submitting an ADA - Accommod
 ations Request form available online at https:tampa.govADARequest (https:t
 ampa.govADARequest). For additional information\, please contact City Coun
 cil Attorney Martin Shelby at Martin.Shelbytampa.gov (mailto:Martin.Shelby
 tampa.gov) or 813-274-7719. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1895
 76
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189576
END:VEVENT
